## Migration from Traditional HTMX

**Before (tightly coupled):**
```html
<form hx-post="/Home/AddTodo" 
      hx-target="#todo-list">
</form>

<div id="todo-list">
    <!-- Only this one list can refresh -->
</div>
```

**After (event-driven):**
```html
<form hx-post="/Home/AddTodo"></form>

<div id="todo-list"
     hx-get="/Home/TodoList"
     hx-trigger="ui.refresh from:body">
</div>

<div id="todo-count"
     hx-get="/Home/TodoCount"
     hx-trigger="ui.refresh from:body">
    <!-- Both refresh independently -->
</div>
```

